///   22. `[writable]` reserve_liquidity_supply
///   23. `[writable]` user_destination_liquidity
///   24. `[optional]` placeholder_user_destination_collateral
///   25. `[]` collateral_token_program
///   26. `[]` liquidity_token_program
///   27. `[]` instruction_sysvar_account
